title: Kyle Dunnigan, Live from Wiseguys in Salt Lake City (ACS August 29)
itunes:title: Kyle Dunnigan, Live from Wiseguys in Salt Lake City (ACS August 29)
description:
Adam comes to you live from Wiseguys in Salt Lake City where he is joined by Kyle Dunnigan who shows off impersonations of Joe Biden, Donald Trump, and Sylvester Stallone. Bryan and Gina join for a round of ‘Blah Blah Blog’. Gina Grad reports the news of the day including: Hitler wine bottles and Nichelle Nichols’ ashes being launched into space. Lastly, Adam riffs on audience-suggested topics in a round of Adam Carolla is Unprepared.
